lead_paragraph: Beyoncé wrapped up her "Formation World Tour" with onstage assists from Kendrick Lamar, Serena Williams and Jay Z, whom she kissed passionately at the end of their performance before an audience of 80,000, including Hugh Jackman, Tyler Perry and Frank Ocean.

headline.print_headline: Jay Z, Serena Williams, Kendrick Help Beyoncé Wrap Up Tour
